C%2Fa%3E%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdoge-elon-musk-vivek-ramaswamy-government-spending-cuts-veterans-nasa-2024-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eslash%20spending%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Musk%20set%20a%20goal%20of%20cutting%20%242%20trillion%20in%20annual%20outlays.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20Musk%20and%20Ramaswamy's%20aims%20for%20DOGE%20could%20lead%20to%20a%20relatively%20early%20win%20with%20bipartisan%20support%3A%20eliminating%20fraud%20in%20federal%20programs%20like%20Medicare.%20In%20a%20recent%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbc.com%2F2024%2F12%2F04%2Fcnbc-transcript-exclusive-doge-co-lead-author-and-former-us-presidential-candidate-vivek-ramaswamy-speaks-with-cnbcs-eamon-javers-and-morgan-brennan-live-from-the-cnbc-cfo-council-summit-in-washington-dc-today.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Einterview%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Ramaswamy%20told%20CNBC%20that%20%26quot%3Bthe%20dirty%20little%20secret%20is%20that%20many%20of%20those%20entitlement%20dollars%20aren't%20even%20going%20to%20people%20who%20they%20were%20supposed%20to%20be%20going%20to%20in%20the%20first%20place.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20are%20hundreds%20of%20billions%20of%20dollars%20of%20savings%20to%20extract%26quot%3B%20through%20basic%20fraud%20prevention%20measures%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMusk%20shared%20that%20sentiment%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fx.com%2Felonmusk%2Fstatus%2F1859081392010801185%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eposting%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20X%20in%20November%3A%20%26quot%3BThe%20sheer%20magnitude%20%26amp%3B%20audacity%20of%20government%20fraud%20is%20mind-blowing!%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EData%20from%20the%20Government%20Accountability%20Office%20showed%20that%20government%20agencies%20have%20made%20about%20%242.7%20trillion%20in%20improper%20payments%20since%202003%2C%20and%20in%20fiscal%20year%202023%2C%20the%20GAO%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.gao.gov%2Fassets%2Fd24106927.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eestimated%3C%2Fa%3E%20agencies%20made%20%24236%20billion%20in%20improper%20payments.%20Notably%2C%20those%20improper%20payments%20include%20other%20categories%20than%20intentional%20fraud%2C%20like%20administrative%20errors%2C%20Orice%20Williams%20Brown%2C%20the%20GAO's%20chief%20operating%20officer%2C%20said%20in%20a%20September%20testimony%20to%20Congress.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhile%20all%20fraudulent%20payments%20are%20considered%20improper%2C%20not%20all%20improper%20payments%20are%20due%20to%20fraud%2C%26quot%3B%20Brown%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20top%20impacted%20agencies%20were%20Medicare%20and%20Medicaid%2C%20which%20the%20GAO%20said%20had%20%2451%20billion%20and%20%2450%20billion%20in%20improper%20payments%2C%20respectively%2C%20followed%20by%20pandemic%20programs%2C%20including%20the%20Paycheck%20Protection%20Program.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EExperts%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20there's%20potential%20for%20DOGE%20to%20make%20progress%20on%20the%20issue%20if%20they%20focus%20on%20effective%20solutions%20like%20system%20modernization%20and%20improved%20data%20analysis%2C%20an%20area%20where%20Ramaswamy%20and%20Musk%20could%20leverage%20their%20Silicon%20Valley%20tech%20experience.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBoth%20fraud%20and%20improper%20payments%20have%20been%20difficult%20for%20the%20government%20to%20address%20because%20of%20%26quot%3Boutdated%20technology%20and%20a%20limited%20focus%20on%20program%20integrity%2C%26quot%3B%20Linda%20Miller%2C%20cofounder%20of%20the%20Program%20Integrity%20Alliance%20%E2%80%94%20a%20group%20that%20focuses%20on%20fraud%20prevention%20in%20the%20government%20%E2%80%94%20told%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20need%20to%20use%20advanced%20technology%20and%20data%20in%20order%20to%20really%20move%20the%20needle%2C%26quot%3B%20Miller%20said.%20%26quot%3BAnd%20the%20government%20is%20not%20using%20advanced%20technology%20and%20data%20to%20solve%20this%20problem.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJetson%20Leder-Luis%2C%20an%20assistant%20professor%20at%20Boston%20University%20and%20researcher%20on%20government%20fraud%2C%20told%20BI%20that%20DOGE%20could%20pursue%20%26quot%3Ba%20lot%20of%20low-hanging%20fruit%20ideas%26quot%3B%20to%20combat%20fraud%20in%20big%20industries%20like%20healthcare.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20DOGE%20has%20the%20opportunity%20to%20make%20big%20strides%20on%20fraud%2C%26quot%3B%20Leder-Luis%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20if%20they%20boost%20enforcement%20funding%20and%20create%20enhanced%20data%20pipelines%2C%20%26quot%3Bthey%20have%20a%20major%20opportunity%20to%20save%20tens%20of%20billions%20of%20dollars.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Trump%20transition%20team%20did%20not%20immediately%20respond%20to%20a%20request%20for%20comment%20from%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2290868abb-1c70-4a19-ae1d-d5728cc8612f%5C%22%3EHow%20government%20programs%20make%20way%20for%20fraud%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20government%20has%20been%20unable%20to%20implement%20widescale%20fraud%20intervention%20in%20recent%20decades%20because%20of%20a%20lack%20of%20resources%20and%20staff%20to%20investigate%20fraud%2C%20and%20a%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Efailure%20to%20modernize%20data%20and%20technology%20systems%2C%20according%20to%20Miller%20and%20Leder-Luis.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20GAO%20found%20that%20the%20government's%20annual%20financial%20losses%20from%20fraud%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Ewere%20between%20%24233%20billion%20and%20%24521%20billion%2C%20based%20on%20data%20from%20fiscal%20years%202018%20through%202022.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMiller%20pointed%20to%20the%20pandemic%20as%20the%20%26quot%3Bperfect%20storm%26quot%3B%20for%20fraud%2C%20with%20the%20Paycheck%20Protection%20Program%20and%20disaster%20loan%20programs%20as%20key%20examples.%20Miller%20said%20that%20all%20that%20aid%20being%20available%2C%20coupled%20with%20limited%20oversight%20at%20the%20government%20level%20during%20a%20national%20emergency%2C%20made%20it%20easier%20for%20fraud%20to%20go%20undetected%3B%20some%20of%20the%20programs%20allowed%20individuals%20to%20self-certify%20their%20loan%20applications%2C%20paving%20the%20way%20for%20misrepresentations.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20lack%20of%20modernization%20of%20our%20digital%20technology%20at%20the%20state%20government%20level%20was%20a%20real%20hindrance%20to%20fraud%20prevention%20during%20the%20pandemic%2C%26quot%3B%20Leder-Luis%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20have%20been%20a%20number%20of%20instances%20where%20individuals%20attempt%2C%20and%20sometimes%20succeed%2C%20to%20game%20the%20system%20and%20score%20welfare%20benefits%20that%20they're%20not%20entitled%20to.%20But%2C%20Miller%20said%2C%20the%20bigger%20concern%20is%20beyond%20the%20individual%20circumstances%3B%20it's%20the%20%26quot%3Blarge-scale%20fraud%20schemes%26quot%3B%20that%20have%20taken%20millions%20of%20dollars%20from%20the%20government.%20For%20example%2C%20the%20FBI%20opened%20an%20investigation%20into%20a%20scheme%20that%20Medicare%20officials%20said%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.washingtonpost.com%2Fhealth%2F2024%2F07%2F02%2Fmedicare-pushes-new-payment-rule-after-alleged-3-billion-fraud-scheme%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edefrauded%20the%20program%3C%2Fa%3E%20out%20of%20%243%20billion%20after%20some%20companies%20billed%20the%20program%20for%20catheters%20patients%20never%20requested%20or%20used.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELawmakers%20and%20the%20Department%20of%20Justice%20have%20worked%20to%20take%20action%20over%20the%20past%20years%20to%20address%20fraud%2C%20including%20with%20the%20federal%20Pandemic%20Response%20Accountability%20Committee%20that%20oversaw%20pandemic-era%20programs.%20Still%2C%20Miller%20said%20that%20while%20agencies%20are%20focused%20on%20getting%20benefits%20to%20the%20beneficiary%2C%20there%20still%20isn't%20enough%20attention%20on%20ensuring%20benefits%20are%20going%20to%20the%20right%20person.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThat's%20the%20kind%20of%20thing%20that%20I%20think%20really%20angers%20Americans%2C%26quot%3B%20Miller%20said.%20%26quot%3BYou%20wonder%2C%20'What%20are%20your%20tax%20dollars%20going%20to%20if%20they're%20not%20stopping%20that%20kind%20of%20fraud%3F'%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2207746e26-b3dc-4c32-81a7-13106d3adc78%5C%22%3EWhere%20DOGE%20can%20play%20a%20role%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EMiller%20said%20she%20expects%20DOGE%20to%20look%20for%20%26quot%3Bquick%20wins%26quot%3B%20soon%20after%20Trump%20takes%20office.%20These%20could%20include%20modernizing%20IT%20systems%20and%20investing%20more%20resources%20into%20fraud%20detection.%20A%20critical%20point%20DOGE%20will%20have%20to%20contend%20with%20is%20that%20cracking%20down%20on%20the%20cost%20of%20fraud%20would%20require%20some%20upfront%20investments.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20can%20be%20very%20helpful%20to%20have%20a%20private%20sector%20lens%20come%20in%20and%20look%20at%20this%2C%26quot%3B%20Miller%20said%2C%20which%20is%20why%20Musk%20and%20Ramaswamy's%20backgrounds%20could%20be%20useful%20in%20introducing%20new%20technology%20to%20government%20systems.%20However%2C%20she%20said%2C%20the%20two%20DOGE%20leaders%20have%20to%20be%20willing%20to%20invest%20in%20new%20fraud%20detection%20systems%20because%2C%20even%20amid%20their%20goals%20to%20slash%20spending%2C%20modernizing%20technology%20is%20not%20going%20to%20be%20free.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20GAO's%20Brown%20also%20outlined%20recommendations%20for%20federal%20agencies%20to%20better%20prevent%20fraud%2C%20including%20using%20external%20data%20from%20third%20parties%20to%20verify%20information%20Americans%20provide%20on%20loan%20and%20insurance%20applications.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20Republicans%20soon%20holding%20control%20of%20both%20Congress%20and%20the%20White%20House%2C%20DOGE's%20recommendations%20to%20Trump%20and%20lawmakers%20would%20likely%20see%20an%20easier%20path%20to%20passage.%20Addressing%20fraud%20has%20also%20seen%20Democratic%20support%3B%20Rep.%20Jamie%20Raskin%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Foversightdemocrats.house.gov%2Fnews%2Fpress-releases%2Franking-member-raskin-introduces-legislation-combat-fraud-government-spending%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eintroduced%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20Government%20Spending%20Oversight%20Committee%20Act%20in%20April%2C%20which%20would%20give%20federal%20inspectors%20general%20tools%20to%20combat%20fraud%20across%20major%20funding%20bills.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20be%20sure%2C%20some%20lawmakers%20and%20experts%20are%20skeptical%20of%20DOGE's%20approach.%20The%20US%20spent%20%246.75%20trillion%20in%20fiscal%20year%202024%2C%20data%20from%20the%20Treasury%20Department%20showed%2C%20and%20it%20wouldn't%20be%20as%20simple%20as%20the%20DOGE%20leaders%20have%20said%20to%20ax%20that%20spending%2C%20lawyers%20told%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20administrative%20law%20requires%20a%20lengthy%20process%20to%20rescind%20regulations%20in%20federal%20agencies%2C%20Musk%20and%20Ramaswamy%20previously%20said%20they%20would%20recommend%20a%20list%20of%20regulations%20that%20Trump%20could%20%26quot%3Bimmediately%20pause.%26quot%3B%20Some%20lawyers%20previously%20said%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felon-musk-ramaswamy-doge-spending-cuts-chevron-doctrine-scotus-trump-2024-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20process%20is%20a%20lot%20more%20complicated%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20the%20DOGE%20leaders%20would%20likely%20face%20legal%20hurdles%20if%20they%20pursued%20that%20route.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMusk%20and%20Ramaswamy%20also%20aren't%20the%20first%20to%20suggest%20cuts%20to%20government%20spending.%20Former%20President%20Ronald%20Reagan's%20Grace%20Commission%2C%20aimed%20at%20eliminating%20waste%20and%20inefficiency%20in%20the%20federal%20government%2C%20eliminated%20%2422%20billion%20in%20social%20welfare%20programs%20that%20ended%20up%20being%20offset%20by%20his%20tax%20cuts%20and%20defense%20spending.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStill%2C%20Leder-Luis%20said%2C%20what%20DOGE%20determines%20as%20%26quot%3Bwaste%26quot%3B%20is%20up%20for%20interpretation%2C%20whereas%20fraud%20is%20illegal%2C%20and%20there's%20support%20across%20the%20aisle%20to%20take%20that%20on.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20we%20lose%20%2450%20billion%20a%20year%20to%20fraud%20in%20just%20the%20healthcare%20system%20alone%2C%20that's%20ultimately%20paid%20for%20by%20us%2C%26quot%3B%20Leder-Luis%20said.%20%26quot%3BThere%20are%20so%20many%20things%20that%20people%20want%20the%20government%20to%20be%20able%20to%20pay%20for%20that%20we%20all%20think%20are%20good%20and%20valuable%2C%20like%20better%20roads%20and%20schools.%20And%20when%20we%20say%2C%20'I'm%20sorry%2C%20we%20can't%20afford%20that%2C'%20well%2C%20we%20are%20affording%20healthcare%20fraud%20instead.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felon-musk-ramaswamy-doge-quick-win-fraud-government-programs-medicare-2024-12%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1734257822000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F675caeba52dd0818d1a73a9a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felon-musk-ramaswamy-doge-quick-win-fraud-government-programs-medicare-2024-12%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Elon%20Musk%20and%20Vivek%20Ramaswamy's%20tech%20backgrounds%20could%20equip%20them%20with%20the%20skills%20to%20slash%20fraud%20in%20government%20programs%2C%20but%20they'll%20need%20to%20invest.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22asheffey%40businessinsider.com%20(Ayelet%20Sheffey)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felon-musk-ramaswamy-doge-quick-win-fraud-government-programs-medicare-2024-12%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'Can't%20celebrate%20EVMs%20when%20you%20win%2C%20blame%20when%20you%20lose'%3A%20Omar%20on%20Congress%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1734257660000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22h