The%20National%20Association%20of%20Realtors%20found%20that%20from%20July%202023%20to%20June%202024%2C%20single%20female%20buyers%20made%20up%2020%25%20of%20all%20homebuyers%2C%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Cem%3Eoutpacing%20single%20male%20buyers%2C%20who%20made%20up%20only%208%25.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20interview%20has%20been%20edited%20for%20length%20and%20clarity.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI'm%20originally%20from%20Cuba.%20My%20parents%20moved%20to%20the%20US%20when%20I%20was%20four%2C%20and%20I%20grew%20up%20in%20Miami.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20left%20at%2018%20for%20college%2C%20then%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmoved-home-after-college-save-money-pros-cons-2024-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emoved%20back%20home%20after%20graduation%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20save%20money%20for%20my%20future.%20I'm%20grateful%20for%20that%20time%2C%20and%20I%20know%20many%20would%20love%20the%20chance%20to%20do%20the%20same.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStill%2C%20I%20didn't%20want%20to%20live%20with%20my%20parents%20forever.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELiving%20at%20home%20meant%20sacrificing%20some%20privacy.%20There%20was%20commentary%20about%20what%20I%20was%20doing%2C%20why%20I%20was%20doing%20it%2C%20and%20how.%20It%20wasn't%20ill-intended%2C%20but%20it%20could%20feel%20like%20a%20lot%20at%20times.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBy%20my%2030s%2C%20the%20decision%20to%20move%20out%20really%20came%20to%20a%20head.%20I%20asked%20myself%3A%20%26quot%3BDoes%20it%20make%20sense%20to%20keep%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fadult-moved-back-home-with-parents-who-pay-bills-rent-2024-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eliving%20at%20home%20to%20save%20money%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20or%20should%20I%20take%20the%20leap%20and%20buy%20my%20own%20place%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20end%2C%20I%20decided%20to%20buy%20a%20home.%20I'd%20never%20truly%20lived%20alone%2C%20and%20I%20wanted%20my%20own%20space%20and%20control%20over%20my%20future.%20Most%20importantly%2