ew%20employees%2C%20labor%20market%20sources%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERecruiters%20said%20that%20has%20already%20made%20the%20job%20market%20more%20competitive%20%E2%80%94%20and%20the%20selection%20will%20get%20even%20tighter%20as%20more%20companies%20adopt%20their%20own%20AI%20tools%20to%20sift%20through%20applicants.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20first%20half%20of%20the%20year%2C%2072%25%20of%20business%20leaders%20said%20they%20were%20raising%20their%20standards%20for%20hiring%20applicants%2C%20according%20to%20a%20report%20from%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fnewsroom.workday.com%2F2024-09-10-Workday-Global-Workforce-Report-Job-Market-Tightens-as-AI-Reshapes-Hiring-Processes%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EWorkday%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Meanwhile%2C%2077%25%20of%20companies%20said%20they%20intended%20to%20scale%20their%20use%20of%20AI%20in%20the%20recruiting%20process%20over%20the%20next%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E63%25%20of%20recruiters%20and%20hiring%20decision%20makers%20said%20they%20already%20used%20AI%20as%20part%20of%20the%20recruiting%20process%2C%20up%20from%2058%25%20last%20year%2C%20a%20separate%20survey%20by%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.jobvite.com%2Femploy-recruiter-nation-report-2024%2F%3Fnab%3D0%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EEmploy%3C%2Fa%3E%20found.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJeff%20Hyman%2C%20a%20veteran%20recruiter%20and%20the%20CEO%20of%20Recruit%20Rockstars%2C%20says%20AI%20software%20is%20growing%20more%20popular%20among%20hiring%20managers%20to%20weed%20through%20stacks%20of%20seemingly%20ideal%20candidates.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIronically%2C%20big%20companies%20are%20using%20AI%20to%20go%20through%20that%20stack%2C%20that%20AI%20has%20brought%20first%20place%2C%20and%20it's%20becoming%20this%20ridiculous%20tit-for-tat%20battle%2C%26quot%3B%20Hyman%20told%20BI%20in%20an%20interview.%20%26quot%3BI%20would%20say%20human%20judgment%20%E2%80%A6%20is%20what%20rules%20the%20day%2C%20but%20certainly%2C%20we%20use%20a%20lot%20of%20software%20to%20reduce%20a%20stack%20from%20500%20to%2050%2C%20because%20you%20got%20to%20start%20somewhere%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20later%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETim%20Sackett%2C%20the%20president%20of%20the%20tech%20staffing%20firm%20HRU%20Technical%20Resources%2C%20says%20some%20firms%20are%20beta-testing%20AI%20software%20that%20can%20allow%20companies%20to%20detect%20fraud%20on%20r%C3%A9sum%C3%A9s%20%E2%80%94%20a%20development%20he%20thinks%20will%20make%20the%20job%20market%20significantly%20more%20competitive.%20That%20technology%20could%20become%20mainstream%20as%20soon%20as%20mid-2025%2C%20he%20speculated%2C%20given%20how%20fast%20AI%20tech%20is%20accelerating.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20just%20going%20to%20get%20worse%2C%26quot%3B%20Sackett%20said%20of%20companies%20being%20more%20selective%20of%20new%20hires.%20%26quot%3BI%20mean%2C%20if%20more%20candidates%20become%20really%20used%20to%20utilizing%20AI%20to%20help%20them%20match%20a%20job%20better%2C%20to%20network%20better%2C%20it's%20just%20going%20to%20happen.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20interview-to-offer%20ratio%20at%20enterprise%20companies%20declined%20to%2064%25%20in%20July%20of%20this%20year%2C%20according%20to%20Employ's%20survey%2C%20which%20indicates%20companies%20are%20interviewing%20fewer%20candidates%20before%20making%20a%20hiring%20decision.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BRecruiters%20are%20scrutinizing%20candidates%20more%20closely%2C%26quot%3B%20Hyman%20adds.%20%26quot%3BMy%20candidate%20interviews%20have%20become%20longer%20and%20more%20in-depth%2C%20designed%20to%20truly%20test%20a%20candidate's%20abilities%20beyond%20a%20polished%20r%C3%A9sum%C3%A9.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22882d0df1-122f-456a-987a-abc30f0aeb84%5C%22%3EInundated%20by%20AI%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EEmployers%20aren't%20big%20fans%20of%20AI%20as%20a%20tool%20for%20candidates%20to%20get%20a%20leg%20up.%20That's%20partly%20because%20it's%20led%20to%20hiring%20systems%20being%20flooded%20with%20applications%20sent%20using%20AI%2C%20Sackett%20and%20Hyman%20said%2C%20which%20has%20made%20hiring%20decisions%20way%20harder.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWorkday%20found%20that%20job%20applications%20grew%20at%20four%20times%20the%20pace%20of%20job%20openings%20in%20the%20first%20half%20of%20this%20year%2C%20with%20recruiters%20processing%20173%20million%20applications%2C%20while%20there%20were%20just%2019%20million%20job%20requisitions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHaving%20too%20many%20candidates%20for%20a%20position%20was%20the%20third%20most%20common%20problem%20recruiters%20faced%20in%202024%2C%20Employ%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHyman%20estimates%20the%20number%20of%20applications%20he%20reviews%20has%20doubled%20over%20the%20last%20year.%20Some%20of%20the%20more%20lucrative%20job%20postings%20are%20seeing%20close%20to%201%2C000%20applications%2C%20he%20said%2C%20whereas%20they%20would%20have%20attracted%20100-200%20applications%20before%20the%20pandemic.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20mean%2C%20a%20stack%20so%20big%2C%20that%20you%20can't%20even%20go%20through%20it%2C%20it's%20just%20not%20even%20possible%20to%20spend%20that%20kind%20of%20time%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECandidates%20sending%20in%20applications%20spruced%20up%20with%20AI%20has%20also%20made%20it%20harder%20to%20determine%20who%20can%20actually%20do%20the%20job.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESackett%20says%20he's%20seen%20an%20increase%20in%20%26quot%3Bfalse%20positive%26quot%3B%20hiring%2C%20where%20a%20worker%20is%20hired%20and%20is%20quickly%20let%20go%20of%20their%20position%20when%20it%20becomes%20clear%20they're%20unable%20to%20do%20the%20job.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20what%20hiring%20managers%20are%20concerned%20about%3A%20Is%20this%20CV%20real%20when%20I'm%20talking%20to%20this%20person%3F%20Am%20I%20talking%20to%20the%20real%20person%20or%20are%20they%20using%20AI%20in%20the%20background%3F%26quot%3B%20Sackett%20said.%20He%20recalled%20one%20client%20he%20worked%20with%20who%20realized%20multiple%20candidates%20responded%20to%20interview%20questions%20in%20the%20same%20way%2C%20likely%20because%20they%20were%20using%20AI%20to%20write%20their%20responses.%20%26quot%3BSo%20I%20think%20people%20just%20want%20to%20know%20that%20I'm%20getting%20what%20I%20think%20I'm%20getting.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjob-search-ai-interviews-resumes-applications-recruiting-labor-market-outlook-2024-12%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1734254101000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F669145e49caa6ed01e011749%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjob-search-ai-interviews-resumes-applications-recruiting-labor-market-outlook-2024-12%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Almost%20three-quarters%20of%20companies%20surveyed%20said%20they%20were%20raising%20hiring%20standards%2C%20as%20recruiters%20say%20AI%20has%20led%20to%20a%20wild%20surge%20in%20the%20number%20of%20applicants.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22jsor%40businessinsider.com%20(Jennifer%20Sor)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A38%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjob-search-ai-interviews-resumes-applications-recruiting-labor-market-outlook-2024-12%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Varun%20shares%20an%20update%20on%20his%20life%20after%20becoming%20a%20father%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1734253792000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-116336020%2Cimgsize-34224.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fvarun-dhawan-shares-an-update-on-his-life-after-becoming-a-father-i-used-to-get-scolded-by-one-woman-before-%2Farticleshow%2F116336033.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiati