%20For%20Life%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%20man%20in%20the%20UK%20is%20facing%20a%20lengthy%20prison%20sentence%20for%20the%20rape%20and%20manslaughter%20of%20a%20vulnerable%20woman%20he%20attacked%20on%20a%20park%20bench.%20Mohamed%20Iidow%2C%2035%2C%20was%20captured%20on%20CCTV%20prowling%20Southall%20Park%20in%20West%20London%2C%20searching%20for%20a%20vulnerable%20target%20before%20approaching%20Natalie%20Shotter%2C%20a%2037-year-old%20mother%20of%20three%2C%20who%20was%20passed%20out%20on%20a%20bench%20after%20a%20night%20out%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noindex%2Cnofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.independent.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fuk%2Fcrime%2Fnhs-old-bailey-london-cctv-hounslow-b2663682.html%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EIndependent%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3Ereported.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20harrowing%20footage%20recorded%20the%20horrific%20assault%2C%20showing%20Iidow%20manipulating%20Natalie's%20%26quot%3Bdeeply%20unconscious%26quot%3B%20body%20to%20repeatedly%20attack%20her%20for%20more%20than%2015%20minutes.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENatalie's%20mother%2C%20Dr%20Cas%20Shotter%20Weetman%2C%20an%20NHS%20cardiology%20practitioner%2C%20has%20called%20for%20urgent%20action%20to%20address%20the%20%26quot%3Bhorrific%26quot%3B%20violence%20against%20women%2C%20emphasizing%20that%20many%20cannot%20walk%20freely%20or%20feel%20safe%20in%20public%20spaces.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20said%3A%20%26quot%3BWe%20need%20to%20change%20our%20thoughts%20about%20how%20we%20behave.%20There%20are%20people%20out%20there%20who%20continue%20to%20act%20in%20a%20very%20deviant%20and%20horrendous%20way%20and%20think%20that%20they%20can%20get%20away%20with%20it.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20moving%20statement%2C%20Dr%20Weetman%20described%20the%20horrific%20ordeal%20of%20having%20to%20watch%20her%20daughter%20being%20raped%2C%20%26quot%3BNo%20mother%20should%20ever%20have%20to%20see%20that.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHearing%20medical%20evidence%20of%20how%20you%20caused%20my%20daughter's%20death%20destroyed%20my%20family.%20I%20felt%20such%20anger%20my%20daughter%20had%20gone%20to%20the%20park%20on%20a%20night%20out%20enjoying%20herself%20and%20was%20assaulted%20by%20a%20predator.%20No%20woman%20should%20have%20to%20fear%20going%20to%20a%20park%20and%20sitting%20on%20a%20bench-%20it%20is%20disgusting.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFurther%2C%20she%20also%20paid%20tribute%20to%20her%20daughter%2C%20saying%20she%20was%20a%20%26quot%3Bbeautiful%20soul%26quot%3B%20and%20the%20%26quot%3Bkindest%20girl%26quot%3B%20who%20would%20help%20others.%20She%20said%20that%20her%20daughter%20was%20a%20%26quot%3Bgreat%20mum%26quot%3B%20to%20her%20three%20children%20aged%205%20to%2019%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noindex%2Cnofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmetro.co.uk%2F2024%2F12%2F13%2Fpredator-raped-nhs-worker-mum-of-three-death-jailed-life-22182149%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EMirror%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3Ereported.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Friday%2C%20Judge%20Richard%20Marks%20KC%20sentenced%20Iidow%20to%20life%20with%20a%20minimum%20term%20of%2010%20years%20and%20eight%20months%2C%20the%20media%20outlet%20reported.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20judge%20said%20that%20taking%20advantage%20of%20Ms%20Shotter%20when%20she%20was%20vulnerable%20and%20unconscious%20was%20%26quot%3Bwicked%20and%20utterly%20reckless%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20judge%20mentioned%20that%20even%20though%20there%20had%20never%20been%20a%20recorded%20case%20before%20of%20someone%20dying%20as%20a%20result%20of%20an%20overstimulation%20of%20the%20nerves%20at%20the%20back%20of%20the%20throat%20causing%20cardiac%20arrest%2C%20there%20was%20a%20'high%20risk'%20that%20she%20would%20suffer%20serious%20harm%20from%20what%20he%20did%20to%20her.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EProsecutor%20Alison%20Morgan%20KC%20said%20during%20the%20trial%20that%20Ms%20Shotter%20had%20died%20of%20a%20heart%20attack%20caused%20by%20Iidow%20raping%20her%20%26quot%3Bagain%20and%20again%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20CCTV%20footage%20showed%20Ms%20Shotter%20sitting%20on%20a%20bench%20with%20a%20different%20man%20when%20Iidow%20walked%20past%20and%20looked%20at%20them.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhat%20was%20the%20defendant%20doing%20there%2C%20what%20was%20he%20seeking%20to%20do%2C%20walking%20up%20and%20down%20the%20paths%20in%20the%20middle%20of%20the%20night%20and%20thinking%20about%20what%20his%20objectives%20must%20have%20been%20-%20seeking%20out%20a%20vulnerable%20woman%20to%20rape%2C%26quot%3B%20Ms%20Morgan%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20convict%20then%20left%20the%20park%20and%20drove%20away%20in%20his%20card%20before%20he%20returned.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20victim%20was%20lying%20down%2C%20showing%20%26quot%3Bno%20clear%20movement%26quot%3B%20for%20around%20half%20an%20hour%20before%20he%20approached%20her%20%26quot%3Bnonchalantly%26quot%3B%2C%20Ms%20Morgan%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20attack%2C%20Ms%20Shotter%20was%20%26quot%3Bdeeply%20unconscious%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20prosecutor%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20CCTV%20further%20showed%20the%20convict%20moving%20Ms%20Shotter's%20body%20around%20in%20different%20positions%20as%20he%20raped%20her.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Shotter%20was%20discovered%20dead%20in%20the%20park%20by%20a%20passerby%20early%20on%20the%20morning%20of%20July%2017%2C%202021.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDNA%20swabs%20taken%20from%20her%20mouth%20matched%20samples%20collected%20from%20Mohamed%20Iidow.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIidow%20was%20arrested%20at%20his%20home%20on%20August%204%2C%202021%2C%20and%20during%20his%20police%20interview%2C%20he%20claimed%20that%20the%20sexual%20activity%20had%20been%20consensual.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Morgan%20told%20jurors%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20prosecution's%20case%20is%20that%20Natalie%20died%20as%20a%20result%20of%20what%20was%20done%20to%20her%20by%20this%20defendant.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BShe%20was%20not%20dead%20at%20the%20time%20when%20the%20defendant%20was%20orally%20raping%20her%2C%20it%20will%20be%20a%20matter%20for%20you%20to%20consider%20-%20that%20this%20defendant%20went%20to%20the%20park%20for%20a%20reason.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe%20would%20not%20have%20sought%20to%20have%20sex%20with%20a%20dead%20body%20for%20over%2015%20minutes%2C%20he%20was%20having%20sex%20with%20someone%20he%20knew%20was%20alive%20but%20was%20deeply%20unconscious%20and%20therefore%20he%20was%20raping%20her.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1734251880000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-12%2Fgcv77obg_mohamed-iidow_625x300_15_December_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fuk-man-who-raped-unconscious-woman-repeatedly-until-she-died-jailed-for-life-7253010%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Ms%20Shotter%20was%20discovered%20dead%20in%20the%20park%20by%20a%20passerby%20early%20on%20the%20morning%20of%20July%2017%2C%202021.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fuk-man-who-raped-unconscious-woman-repeatedly-until-she-died-jailed-for-life-7253010%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%2219%20Maharashtra%20BJP%20MLAs%2C%20Including%203%20Women%2C%20Likely%20To%20Take%20Oath%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EAfter%20weeks%20of%20hectic%20parleys%20over%20the%20Chief%20Minister%20chair%20and%20then%20the%20'who-gets-what-ministry'%2C%20the%20new%20BJP-led%20government%20in%20Maharashtra%20is%20all%20set%20to%20expand%20its%20Cabinet%20today.%20The%20BJP%2C%20which%20holds%20the%20highest%20share%20of%20Cabinet%20berths%2C%20will%20likely%20induct%2019%20MLAs%2C%20including%20three%20women%20leaders%2C%20sources%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20list%20of%20probable%20BJP%20leaders%20are%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPankaja%20Munde%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeghna%20Bord