20discontent%20among%20INDIA%20bloc%20partners%20with%20the%20Congress%2C%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20Chief%20Minister%20Omar%20Abdullah%20has%20asked%20the%20party%20to%20justify%20its%20leadership%20role%20in%20the%20alliance%20instead%20of%20taking%20it%20for%20granted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAbdullah%2C%20while%20recognising%20the%20Congress'%20significant%20position%20as%20a%20pan-India%20party%20and%20the%20largest%20opposition%20in%20Parliament%2C%20emphasised%20that%20leadership%20%26quot%3Bhas%20to%20be%20earned%26quot%3B%20and%20cannot%20be%20taken%20for%20granted.%20He%20also%20suggested%20that%20the%20party%20should%20raise%20the%20issue%20of%20restoration%20of%20statehood%20in%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBy%20virtue%20of%20being%20the%20single%20largest%20party%20in%20Parliament%2C%20and%20also%20having%20the%20leader%20of%20opposition%20in%20both%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20and%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%2C%20the%20fact%20that%20they%20have%20a%20pan-India%20footprint%2C%20which%20no%20other%20party%20can%20lay%20claim%20to%2C%20they%20are%20natural%20sort%20of%20leaders%20of%20an%20opposition%20movement%2C%26quot%3B%20Abdullah%20told%20PTI%20in%20his%20first%20interview%20after%20becoming%20the%20chief%20minister%20in%20October.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYet%20there%20is%20a%20sense%20of%20disquiet%20among%20some%20of%20the%20allies%20because%20they%20feel%20the%20Congress%20is%20%26quot%3Bnot%20doing%20enough%20to%20justify%20it%20or%20to%20earn%20it%20or%20to%20keep%20it.%20That's%20something%20the%20Congress%20might%20wish%20to%20consider.%26quot%3B%20Still%2C%20Abdullah%20praised%20former%20Congress%20president%20Sonia%20Gandhi%2C%20describing%20her%20as%20a%20leader%20of%20unparalleled%20stature%20within%20the%20opposition%20alliance.%20%26quot%3BWhen%20the%20INDIA%20bloc%20comes%20together%2C%20she%20plays%20an%20important%20leadership%20role%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAbdullah%20chose%20not%20to%20give%20a%20direct%20answer%20to%20a%20question%20about%20statements%20made%20by%20leaders%20like%20Sharad%20Pawar%20or%20Lalu%20Yadav%20favouring%20West%20Bengal%20Chief%20Minister%20Mamata%20Banerjee%20as%20a%20better%20leader%20but%20highlighted%20the%20INDIA%20bloc's%20lack%20of%20consistent%20engagement%2C%20warning%20that%20the%20coalition%20risks%20becoming%20a%20mere%20election-time%20convenience.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAbdullah%20stressed%20the%20need%20for%20sustained%20interactions%20beyond%20the%20electoral%20cycle%2C%20noting%20that%20the%20alliance's%20current%20approach%20appears%20sporadic%20and%20ineffective.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOur%20existence%20can't%20just%20be%20about%20six%20months%20before%20Parliament%20elections.%20Our%20existence%20has%20to%20be%20something%20more%20than%20that.%20The%20last%20time%20we%20met%20was%20when%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20results%20had%20only%20just%20come%20out.%20There%20has%20been%20no%20formal%20or%20informal%20sort%20of%20work%20that%20has%20been%20done%20for%20the%20INDIA%20bloc%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAbdullah%2C%20who%20is%20the%20vice%20president%20of%20the%20National%20Conference%2C%20also%20stressed%20the%20importance%20of%20establishing%20a%20structured%20communication%20framework.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20need%20to%20have%20a%20programme%20of%20regular%20interactions%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20explained%2C%20adding%20%26quot%3Bnot%20that%20you%20just%20come%20alive%20once%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%20are%20announced%20and%20suddenly%20start%20talking%20and%20trying%20to%20work%20things%20out%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAbdullah's%20comments%20suggest%20underlying%20tensions%20within%20the%20opposition%20alliance%2C%20indicating%20that%20infrequent%20meetings%20could%20potentially%20magnify%20minor%20disagreements.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20we%20had%20a%20more%20regular%20process%20of%20interaction%2C%20perhaps%20these%20smaller%20irritants%20wouldn't%20assume%20larger%20proportions%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAbdullah%20has%20also%20not%20been%20very%20happy%20with%20the%20electoral%20alliance%20his%20National%20Conference%20party%20formed%20with%20the%20Congress%20before%20the%20Jammu-Kashmir%20assembly%20elections%2C%20where%20it%20failed%20to%20pull%20its%20weight%20during%20campaigning.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20NC%20won%2041%20seats%20while%20Congress%20got%20six.%20Observers%20noted%20that%20Congress%20leaders%20did%20little%20work%20during%20the%20campaigning%2C%20and%20left%20all%20the%20heavy%20lifting%20to%20the%20NC.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EINDIA%20bloc%20was%20formed%20as%20a%20combined%20opposition%20to%20stop%20the%20ruling%20BJP%20juggernaut%20but%20has%20failed%20to%20make%20much%20dent.%20Despite%20its%20good%20showing%20in%20the%20parliamentary%20elections%2C%20the%20Congress%20and%20its%20allies%20have%20failed%20miserably%20in%20two%20recent%20assembly%20elections%20-%20Haryana%20and%20Maharashtra.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAbdullah's%20comments%20are%20further%20proof%20of%20the%20discontent%20within%20the%20INDIA%20bloc%20and%20the%20challenges%20it%20faces%20in%20countering%20the%20BJP%20in%20future%20political%20engagements.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20candid%20assessment%20of%20recent%20electoral%20debacles%20for%20Congress%2C%20Abdullah%20highlighted%20the%20growing%20strains%20within%20political%20alliances%2C%20particularly%20focusing%20on%20the%20Congress%20party's%20electoral%20performance%20and%20seat%20distribution%20strategies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Congress%20needs%20to%20critically%20examine%20its%20strike%20rate%20and%20learn%20lessons%20applicable%20to%20future%20elections%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERecurring%20patterns%20of%20alliance%20discomfort%20have%20been%20observed%20across%20multiple%20states%2C%20including%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%2C%20Jharkhand%2C%20and%20Maharashtra%2C%20he%20said%20adding%20these%20tensions%20have%20reportedly%20contributed%20to%20the%20breakdown%20of%20potential%20alliances%2C%20such%20as%20the%20failure%20to%20collaborate%20between%20the%20Aam%20Aadmi%20Party%20(AAP)%20and%20Congress%20in%20Delhi%2C%20despite%20previous%20parliamentary%20election%20cooperation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAsked%20whether%20the%20Congress%20could%20get%20a%20ministerial%20berth%20in%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%2C%20Abdullah%20drew%20parallels%20with%20past%20power-sharing%20experiences%2C%20referencing%20the%20United%20Progressive%20Alliance%20(UPA)%20government%20under%20Manmohan%20Singh%20when%20ministerial%20portfolios%20were%20determined%20by%20the%20number%20of%20legislators%20a%20party%20had.%20At%20that%20time%20Abdullah's%20father%2C%20Farooq%20Abdullah%2C%20got%20a%20minor%20ministry.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSo%20if%20that%20worked%20for%20us%20then%2C%20it%20works%20for%20the%20Congress%20now.%20And%20the%20fact%20is%20that%20as%20a%20Union%20Territory%2C%20we%20are%20limited%20to%20having%20nine%20ministers.%20With%20nine%20ministers%20including%20the%20chief%20minister%2C%20I%20was%20not%20in%20a%20position%20to%20offer%20the%20Congress%20more%20than%20we%20did%20offer%20them%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20party%20has%20indicated%20that%20their%20participation%20in%20the%20government%20will%20be%20contingent%20on%20J-K%20regaining%20its%20statehood%2C%20signalling%20potential%20future%20realignment%20of%20political%20strategies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSo%20for%20the%20time%20being%2C%20they've%20made%20it%20very%20clear%20that%20so%20long%20as%20J-K%20remains%20a%20Union%20Territory%2C%20they'll%20stay%20out.%20Once%20statehood%20is%20restored%2C%20then%20that%20will%20change.%20So%20we%20hope%20that%20when%20they're%20done%20fighting%20in%20Parliament%20for%20other%20things%2C%20they%20will%20also%20talk%20about%20statehood%20for%20J-K.%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20