2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fbox-office%2Fallu-arjuns-pushpa-2-becomes-the-third-biggest-hit-of-indian-cinema-displacing-ram-charan-and-ntr-jrs-rrr%2Farticleshow%2F116331564.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F116331564.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EAllu%20Arjun's%20%26quot%3BPushpa%202%20-%20The%20Rule%26quot%3B%20has%20stormed%20the%20box%20office%2C%20becoming%20the%20third%20biggest%20Indian%20cinema%20hit%2C%20surpassing%20%26quot%3BRRR.%26quot%3B%20The%20film's%20impressive%20Rs%20824.5%20crore%20collection%20in%20ten%20days%20solidifies%20Arjun's%20superstar%20status%20and%20sets%20its%20sights%20on%20challenging%20%26quot%3BKGF%3A%20Chapter%202%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3BBaahubali%202.%26quot%3B%20A%20third%20installment%2C%20%26quot%3BPushpa%203%20-%20The%20Rampage%2C%26quot%3B%20is%20already%20announced.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20Entertainment%20Desk%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22What%20Is%20Drug%20Captagon%2C%20How%20Is%20It%20Linked%20To%20Syria's%20Fallen%20Assad%20Regime%3F%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20fall%20of%20the%20al-Assad%20regime%20in%20Syria%2C%20large%20stockpiles%20of%20the%20illicit%20drug%20captagon%20have%20reportedly%20been%20uncovered.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theguardian.com%2Fworld%2F2024%2Fdec%2F13%2Fsyrian-rebels-captagon-drug-haul-exports-fenethylline%5C%22%3EThe%20stockpiles%2C%20found%20by%20Syrian%20rebels%2C%20are%20believed%20to%20be%20linked%20to%20al-Assad%20military%20headquarters%2C%20%3C%2Fa%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fedition.cnn.com%2F2024%2F12%2F11%2Fmiddleeast%2Fsyria-captagon-assad-factory-video-intl%2Findex.html%5C%22%3Eimplicating%20the%20fallen%20regime%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20drug's%20manufacture%20and%20distribution.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20as%20we'll%20see%2C%20captagon%20was%20once%20a%20pharmaceutical%20drug%2C%20similar%20to%20some%20of%20the%20legally%20available%20stimulants%20we%20still%20use%20today%20for%20conditions%20including%20attention-deficit%20hyperactivity%20disorder%20(ADHD).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3ECaptagon%20was%20once%20a%20pharmaceutical%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECaptagon%20is%20the%20original%20brand%20name%20of%20an%20old%20synthetic%20pharmaceutical%20stimulant%20originally%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpmc.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov%2Farticles%2FPMC10977473%2F%5C%22%3Emade%20in%20Germany%20in%20the%201960s%3C%2Fa%3E.%20It%20was%20an%20alternative%20to%20amphetamine%20and%20methamphetamine%2C%20which%20were%20both%20used%20as%20medicines%20at%20the%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20drug%20has%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpubchem.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov%2Fcompound%2FFenethylline%5C%22%3Eactive%20ingredient%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2FFenethylline%5C%22%3Efenethylline%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20was%20initially%20marketed%20for%20conditions%20including%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpmc.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov%2Farticles%2FPMC10977473%2F%5C%22%3EADHD%20and%20the%20sleeping%20disorder%20narcolepsy%3C%2Fa%3E.%20It%20had%20a%20similar%20use%20to%20some%20of%20the%20legally%20available%20stimulants%20we%20still%20use%20today%2C%20such%20as%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fadf.org.au%2Fdrug-facts%2Fdexamphetamine%2F%5C%22%3Edexamphetamine%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECaptagon%20has%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpmc.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov%2Farticles%2FPMC10977473%2F%23%3A%257E%3Atext%3DCaptagon%252C%2520related%2520to%2520amphetamines%252C%2520enhances%2C%252Dbeing%252C%2520and%2520increase%2520stamina.%5C%22%3Esimilar%20effects%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20amphetamines.%20It%20increases%20dopamine%20in%20the%20brain%2C%20leading%20to%20feelings%20of%20wellbeing%2C%20pleasure%20and%20euphoria.%20It%20also%20improves%20focus%2C%20concentration%20and%20stamina.%20But%20it%20has%20a%20lot%20of%20unwanted%20side%20effects%2C%20such%20as%20low-level%20psychosis.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20drug%20was%20originally%20sold%20mostly%20in%20the%20Middle%20East%20and%20parts%20of%20Europe.%20It%20was%20available%20over%20the%20counter%20(without%20a%20prescription)%20in%20Europe%20for%20a%20short%20time%20before%20it%20became%20prescription-only.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20approved%20only%20briefly%20in%20the%20United%20States%20before%20becoming%20a%20controlled%20substance%20in%20the%201980s%2C%20but%20was%20still%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.euda.europa.eu%2Fpublications%2Femcdda-papers%2Fcaptagon-understanding-todays-illicit-market_en%5C%22%3Elegal%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20the%20treatment%20of%20narcolepsy%20in%20many%20European%20countries%20until%20relatively%20recently.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.drugsandalcohol.ie%2F39540%2F1%2Fcaptagon-report_7september2023.pdf%5C%22%3EInternational%20Narcotics%20Control%20Board%3C%2Fa%3E%20pharmaceutical%20manufacture%20of%20Captagon%20had%20stopped%20by%202009.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20illicit%20trade%20took%20over%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20illegally%20manufactured%20version%20is%20usually%20referred%20to%20as%20captagon%20(with%20a%20small%20c).%20It%20is%20sometimes%20called%20%E2%80%9C%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpmc.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov%2Farticles%2FPMC10977473%2F%5C%22%3Echemical%20courage%3C%2Fa%3E%E2%80%9D%20because%20it%20is%20thought%20to%20be%20used%20by%20soldiers%20in%20war-torn%20areas%20of%20the%20Middle%20East%20to%20help%20give%20them%20focus%20and%20energy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20instance%2C%20it's%20been%20reportedly%20found%20on%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.psychiatrictimes.com%2Fview%2Fthe-captagon-controversy-and-why-it-captivates%5C%22%3Ebodies%20of%20Hamas%20soldiers%3C%2Fa%3E%20during%20the%20conflict%20with%20Israel.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIts%20manufacture%20is%20relatively%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpmc.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov%2Farticles%2FPMC10977473%2F%23%3A%257E%3Atext%3DOther%2520side%2520effects%2520are%2520tachycardia%2Cinterest%2520in%2520food%2520%255B47%255D%5C%22%3Estraightforward%20and%20inexpensive%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20making%20it%20an%20obvious%20target%20for%20the%20black-market%20drug%20trade.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpmc.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov%2Farticles%2FPMC10977473%2F%23%3A%257E%3Atext%3DOther%2520side%2520effects%2520are%2520tachycardia%2Cinterest%2520in%2520food%2520%255B47%255D%5C%22%3EBlack-market%20captagon%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20now%20nearly%20exclusively%20manufactured%20in%20Syria%20and%20surrounding%20countries%20such%20as%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fglobalinitiative.net%2Fanalysis%2Fcaptagon%2F%5C%22%3ELebanon%3C%2Fa%3E.%20It's%20mostly%20used%20in%20the%20Middle%20East%2C%20including%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Fworld%2Fmiddle-east%2Fcaptagon-drug-fuelling-gulf-party-scene-syrias-finances-2023-05-09%2F%5C%22%3Erecreationally%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20some%20Gulf%20states.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20one%20of%20the%20most%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpmc.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov%2Farticles%2FPMC10977473%2F%23%3A%257E%3Atext%3DOther%2520side%2520effects%2520are%2520tachycardia%2Cinterest%2520in%2520food%2520%255B47%255D%5C%22%3Ecommonly%20used%20illicit%20drugs%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20Syria.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fstorage.googleapis.com%2Fkaram_viz%2Fkaram_online_publications%2FSky%2520High-The%2520Ensuing%2520Narcotics%2520Crisis%2520in%2520Arab%2520Asia%2520and%2520the%2520Role%2520of%2520the%2520Assad%2520Regime%252013%2520June%25202023.pdf%3Fitid%3Dlk_inline_enhanced-template%5C%22%3Erecent%20report%3C%2Fa%3E%20suggests%20captagon%20generated%20more%20than%20US%247.3%20billion%20in%20Syria%20and%20Lebanon%20between%202020%20and%202022%20(about%20%242.4%20billion%20a%20year).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20we%20know%20about%20illicit%20drugs%20generally%20is%20that%20any%20seizures%20or%20crackdowns%20on%20manufacturing%20or%20sale%20have%20a%20very%20limited%20impact%20on%20the%20drug%20market%20because%20another%20manufacturer%20or%20distributor%20pops%20up%20to%20meet%20demand.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%20in%20all%20likelihood%2C%20given%20the%20size%20of%20the%20captagon%20market%20in%20the%20Middle%20East%2C%20these%20latest%20drug%20discoveries%20and%20seizures%20are%20likely%20to%20reduce%20manufacture%20only%20for%20a%20short%20time.%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20Conversation%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221%5C%22%20referrerpolicy%3D%5C%22no-referrer-when-downgrade%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcounter.theconversation.com%2Fcontent%2F245935%2Fcount.gif%3Fdistributor%3Drepublish-lightbox-basic%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cspan%3E(Author%3A%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftheconversation.com%2Fprofiles%2Fnicole-lee-81635%5C%22%3ENicole%20Lee%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Adjunct%20Professor%20at%20the%20National%20Drug%20Research%20Institute%20(Melbourne%20based)%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftheconversation.com%2Finstitutions%2Fcurtin-university-873%5C%22%3ECurtin%20University%3C%2Fa%3E)%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20article%20is%20republished%20from%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftheconversation.com%5C%22%3EThe%20Conversation%3C%2Fa%3E%20under%20a%20Creative%20Commons%20license.%20Read%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftheconversation.com%2Fwhat-is-the-drug-captagon-and-how-is-it-linked-to-syrias-fallen-assad-regime-245935%5C%22%3Eoriginal%20article%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1734237300000%2C%22visua