20all%20the%20time%20%E2%80%94%20AI%20is%20going%20to%20have%20an%20impact%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BIf%20your%20job%20requires%20you%20to%20think%20%E2%80%94%20AI%20won't%20have%20much%20of%20an%20impact.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECuban%2C%20the%20CEO%20of%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmark-cuban-cost-plus-strategy-disrupt-drug-pricing-big-pharma-2024-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECost%20Plus%20Drugs%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20an%20online%20prescription%20service%2C%20said%20workers%20must%20supervise%20AI%20and%20ensure%20that%20the%20data%20the%20models%20are%20being%20trained%20on%20and%20the%20resulting%20output%20are%20correct.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20takes%20intellectual%20capacity.%20So%20somebody%20who%20understands%20what%20the%20goal%20is%2C%20somebody%20who's%20been%20doing%20this%20for%20years%2C%20has%20got%20to%20be%20able%20to%20input%20feedback%20on%20everything%20that%20the%20models%20collect%20and%20are%20trained%20on%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BYou%20don't%20just%20assume%20the%20model%20knows%20everything.%20You%20want%20somebody%20to%20check%20%E2%80%94%20to%20grade%20their%20responses%20%E2%80%94%20and%20make%20corrections.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAI's%20recent%20advancement%20has%20raised%20existential%20questions%20on%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fleaders-discuss-ai-technology-transform-company-workflows-unlock-employee-potential-2024-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efuture%20of%20work%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.weforum.org%2Fpublications%2Fthe-future-of-jobs-report-2023%2Fdigest%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EWorld%20Economic%20Forum%3C%2Fa%3E%20reported%20in%202023%20that%20employers%20expected%2044%25%20of%20workers'%20skills%20to%20be%20%26quot%3Bdisrupted%26quot%3B%20within%20five%20years%2C%20requiring%20a%20massive%20effort%20on%20worker%20retraining.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20McKin