ong%20citizens.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOfficials%20from%20the%20Federal%20Bureau%20of%20Investigation%20and%20the%20Department%20of%20Homeland%20Security%20told%20reporters%20on%20Saturday%20that%20they%20were%20still%20investigating%20but%20had%20no%20evidence%20the%20aircraft%20pose%20a%20threat%20to%20the%20public%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Eor%20are%20connected%20to%20a%20foreign%20adversary.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBut%20...%20we%20don't%20know%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20spokesperson%20from%20the%20Joint%20Staff%20said%20in%20a%20Saturday%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.defense.gov%2FNews%2FNews-Stories%2FArticle%2FArticle%2F4002374%2Fjoint-staff-addresses-drones-over-new-jersey-military-installations%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Estatement%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20confirmed%20sightings%20at%20two%20military%20bases%20in%20New%20Jersey.%20%26quot%3BWe%20have%20not%20been%20able%20to%20locate%20or%20identify%20the%20operators%20or%20the%20points%20of%20origin.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENew%20York%20Gov.%20Kathy%20Hochul%20also%20spoke%20out%20on%20Saturday%2C%20calling%20for%20more%20federal%20oversight%20of%20drones.%20%26quot%3BThis%20has%20gone%20too%20far%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHere's%20everything%20we%20know%20so%20far%20about%20the%20%26quot%3Bmystery%20drones.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2255b52fb7-4dc9-4047-b0a3-0cdf5410f2f3%5C%22%3EWhere%20have%20residents%20reported%20unidentified%20aircraft%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EResidents%20and%20officials%20have%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.forbes.com%2Fsites%2Fstephenpastis%2F2024%2F12%2F13%2Fmystery-drones-over-new-jersey-and-nearby-states-trump-weighs-in-as-more-sightings-reported-updating%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ereported%20spotting%20unidentified%20aircraft%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Ebelieved%20to%20be%20drones%2C%20flying%20above%20New%20Jersey%2C%20New%20York%2C%20Connecticut%2C%20Maryland%2C%20Massachusetts%2C%20and%20Pennsylvania%20in%20recent%20weeks.%20The%20first%20sightings%2C%20the%20FBI%20said%2C%20were%20on%20November%2018.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENew%20Jersey%20Gov.%20Phil%20Murphy%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.foxnews.com%2Fvideo%2F6365767557112%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etold%20reporters%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20Monday%20that%20some%20of%20the%20suspected%20drones%20are%20%26quot%3Bvery%20sophisticated%26quot%3B%20and%20can%20%26quot%3Bgo%20dark%26quot%3B%20the%20%26quot%3Bminute%20you%20get%20eyes%20on%20them.%26quot%3B%20Others%20have%20described%20the%20aircraft%20as%20bigger%20than%20normal%20hobby%20drones%20and%20able%20to%20avoid%20detection.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20something%20we're%20taking%20deadly%20seriously%20and%20we've%20gotten%20good%20cooperation%20out%20of%20the%20feds%2C%20but%20we%20need%20more%2C%26quot%3B%20Murphy%20told%20reporters.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDrones%20have%20been%20spotted%20near%20Picatinny%20Arsenal%20and%20Naval%20Weapons%20Station%20Earle%2C%20both%20military%20bases%20in%20New%20Jersey%2C%20and%20an%20airport%20in%20New%20York%20serving%20the%20public%20and%20the%20military.%20However%2C%20officials%20have%20stressed%20such%20sightings%20are%20routine.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20not%20a%20new%20issue%20for%20us.%20We've%20had%20to%20deal%20with%20drone%20incursions%20over%20our%20bases%20for%20quite%20a%20time%20now%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Joint%20Staff%20spokesperson%20said%20Saturday.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20something%20that%20we%20routinely%20respond%20to%20in%20each%20and%20every%20case%20when%20reporting%20is%20cited.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20have%20also%20been%20reports%20of%20suspected%20drones%20following%20a%20US%20Coast%20Guard%20vessel%2C%20as%20well%20as%20local%20police%20statements%20on%20the%20presence%20of%20unidentified%20aircraft%20near%20critical%20infrastructure.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUS%20Northern%20Command%2C%20which%20is%20responsible%20for%20overseeing%20the%20protection%20of%20the%20US%20homeland%2C%20said%20it%20was%20%26quot%3Baware%20and%20monitoring%20the%20reports%20of%20unauthorized%20drone%20flights%20in%20the%20vicinity%20of%20military%20installations%20in%20New%20Jersey%2C%26quot%3B%20including%20around%20the%20Picatinny%20Arsenal%20and%20Naval%20Weapons%20Station%20Earle.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20latest%20sightings%20were%20in%20Connecticut%2C%20according%20to%20a%20statement%20on%20Friday%20from%20State%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3ESen.%20Tony%20Hwang.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%227da00725-e85a-4595-b96c-1054845f0ce0%5C%22%3EWhat%20officials%20are%20saying%20about%20these%20mystery%20drones%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EPresident-elect%20Donald%20Trump%20said%20Friday%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftruthsocial.com%2F%40realDonaldTrump%2Fposts%2F113647906240301335%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETruth%20Social%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20the%20drones%20%26quot%3Bcan't%20be%20done%20without%20our%20government's%20knowledge%26quot%3B%20and%20suggested%20they%20be%20shot%20down.%20Other%20officials%20have%20expressed%20concern%20about%20shooting%20them%20down%20due%20to%20the%20threat%20to%20local%20populations%20of%20falling%20debris.%20Neither%20kinetic%20nor%20electronic%20warfare%20methods%20are%20particularly%20ideal%20near%20civilian%20areas.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERep.%20Jeff%20Van%20Drew%20of%20New%20Jersey%20said%20on%20Fox%20News%20on%20Wednesday%20that%20the%20drones%20came%20from%20an%20Iranian%20%26quot%3Bmothership%26quot%3B%20off%20the%20East%20Coast%20of%20the%20United%20States%2C%20citing%20%26quot%3Bvery%20high%20sources.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPentagon%20Press%20Secretary%20Sabrina%20Singh%20rejected%20that%20assertion%20in%20a%20press%20conference%20later%20that%20day%2C%20saying%20that%20%26quot%3Bthere%20is%20no%20Iranian%20ship%20off%20the%20coast%20of%20the%20United%20States%2C%20and%20there's%20no%20so-called%20mothership%20launching%20drones%20toward%20the%20United%20States.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESingh%20said%20that%20the%20Pentagon%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmystery-drones-over-nj-not-from-an-iranian-mothership-pentagon-2024-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehas%20no%20evidence%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20the%20reported%20drone%20sightings%20are%20the%20work%20of%20a%20foreign%20adversary.%20While%20Iran%20does%20have%20vessels%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Firan-new-drone-carrier-left-home-port-images-2024-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethat%20can%20carry%20drones%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20they%20were%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsatellite-images-iranian-drone-carriers-far-from-us-amid-mystery-2024-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Espotted%20off%20its%20southern%20coast%3C%2Fa%3E%20as%20recently%20as%20Thursday%20%E2%80%94%20debunking%20Van%20Drew's%20claims.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20doubled%20down%20on%20Thursday%2C%20saying%20the%20government%20isn't%20telling%20the%20truth.%20The%20congressman%20said%20it%20could%20be%20another%20ship%20belonging%20to%20another%20foe.%20A%20Department%20of%20Homeland%20Security%20official%20said%20Saturday%20that%20there%20is%20no%20evidence%20of%20any%20foreign-based%20involvement%20in%20sending%20drones%20ashore%20from%20vessels%20in%20the%20area.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJohn%20Kirby%2C%20a%20White%20House%20National%20Security%20Council%20spokesperson%2C%20said%20on%20Thursday%20the%20United%20States%20had%20%26quot%3Bno%20evidence%26quot%3B%20that%20the%20reported%20drone%20sightings%20are%20a%20public%20safety%20threat.%20He%20added%20that%20the%20government%20believes%20some%20of%20the%20suspected%20drones%20were%20actually%20crewed%20aircraft%20operating%20lawfully.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKirby%20also%20said%20that%20the%20federal%20government%20had%20not%20been%20able%20to%20confirm%20any%20of%20the%20sightings.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20to%20reporters%20Saturday%2C%20an%20FBI%20official%20said%20that%20the%20bureau%20had%20received%205%2C000%20tips%20through%20a%20national%20tip%20line%2C%20but%20of%20those%20reports%2C%20fewer%20than%20100%20were%20deemed%20worthy%20of%20more%20investigation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe're%20doing%20our%20best%20to%20find%20the%20origin%20of%20those%20drone%20activities%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20FBI%20official%20said.%20%26quot%3BBut%20I%20think%20there%20has%20been%20a%20slight%20overreaction.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELocal%20officials%2C%20meanwhile%2C%20are%20calling%20for%20more%20information.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENew%20York%20Gov.%20Kathy%20Hochul%20said%20in%20a%20statement%20on%20Saturday%20that%20runways%20at%20Stewart%20International%20Airport%20in%20Orange%20County%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Ewere%20shut%20down%20for%20an%20hour%20due%20to%20unidentified%20drone%20activity.%20Hochul%20called%20on%20Congress%20to%20strengthen%20the%20Federal%20Aviation%20Administration's%20oversight%20of%20drones%20and%20provide%20counter-unmanned%20aircraft%20equipment%20to%20local%20law%20enforcement.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMayors%20of%2021%20towns%20in%20New%20Jersey%20also%20sent%20a%20letter%20to%20Gov.%20Murphy%20on%20Monday%20demanding%20more%20transparency.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDespite%20inquiries%20made%20to%20relevant%20authorities%2C%20we%20have%20yet%20to%20receive%20satisfactory%20answers%20about%20the%20purpose%2C%20operators%2C%20or%20safety%20protocols%20governing%20these%20flights%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20letter%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20FBI%20said%20that%20it's%20leading%20the%20investigation.%20Local%20law%20enforcement%20agencies%20are%20also%20investigating.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2263ed5e89-2144-4745-8810-7c419e8f4528%5C%22%3EPrevious%20unidentified%20flying%20objects%20and%20drone%20sightings%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20have%20been%20a%20number%20of%20sightings%20of%20suspected%20drones%20and%20other%20unusual%20flying%20objects%20over%20military%20installations%20in%20recent%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20February%202023%2C%20for%20example%2C%20the%20United%20States%20shot%20down%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fobjects-shot-down-over-alaska-canada-ufo-interfered-f22-sensors-2023-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethree%20unidentified%20objects%3C%2Fa%3E%20flying%20over%20American%20airspace%20over%20the%20course%20of%20three%20days.%20The%20incidents%20followed%20the%20US%20takedown%20of%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fobjects-shot-down-over-alaska-canada-ufo-interfered-f22-sensors-2023-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Espy%20balloon%3C%2Fa%3E%20off%20the%20coast%20of%20North%20Carolina%20the%20government%20said%20came%20from%20China.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20for%20drone%20activity%2C%20The%20Wall%20Street%20Journal%20reported%20in%20October%20that%20fleets%20of%20drones%20had%20been%20spotted%20over%20a%20military%20base%20in%20Virginia%20and%20the%20Energy%20Department's%20Nevada%20National%20Security%20Site%20the%20year%20prior.%20Retired%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EUS%20Air%20Force%20Gen.%20Mark%20Kelly%2C%20until%20March%20of%20this%20year%20the%20head%20of%20Air%20Combat%20Command%2C%20said%20that%20he%20learned%20about%20the%20sightings%20in%20December%202023%2C%20when%20officials%20at%20Langley%20Air%20Force%20Base%20in%20Virginia%20reported%20seeing%20dozens%20of%20drones%20flying%20over%20the%20base%20at%20night.%20It's%20unclear%20who%20was%20behind%20those%20incidents.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20federal%20government%20says%20that%20the%20latest%20sightings%20are%20not%20the%20work%20of%20adversaries%20or%20a%20public%20security%20threat%2C%20multiple%20recent%20incidents%20near%20bases%20have%20raised%20national%20security%20concerns.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20instance%2C%20federal%20authorities%20on%20Monday%20charged%20a%20Chinese%20citizen%20residing%20in%20California%2C%20Yinpiao%20Zhou%2C%20with%20failure%20to%20register%20a%20non-transportation%20aircraft%20and%20violation%20of%20national%20defense%20airspace.%20The%20Justice%20Department%20accused%20Zhou%20of%20using%20a%20drone%20to%20photograph%20Vandenberg%20Space%20Force%20Base%20in%20Santa%20Barbara%20County%20on%20November%2030.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPolice%20arrested%20Zhou%20at%20the%20San%20Francisco%20International%20Airport%20before%20he%20boarded%20a%20China-bound%20flight.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnother%20man%2C%20Fengyun%20Shi%2C%20a%20Chinese%20national%2C%20was%20sentenced%20to%20six%20months%20in%20federal%20prison%20in%20October%20for%20photographing%20classified%20US%20Navy%20ships%20with%20a%20drone%20in%20Virginia.%20Fengyun%2C%20a%20student%20at%20the%20University%20of%20Minnesota%2C%20pleaded%20guilty%20to%20two%20misdemeanor%20counts%20of%20unauthorized%20use%20of%20aircraft%20for%20the%20unlawful%20photographing%20of%20a%20designated%20installation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20FBI%20official%20who%20spoke%20to%20reporters%20on%20Saturday%20said%20about%20the%20most%20recent%20sightings%3A%20%26quot%3BWe%20are%20doing%20everything%20we%20can%2C%20alongside%20our%20partners%2C%20to%20understand%20what%20is%20happening%20and%20whether%20or%20not%20there%20is%20more%20nefarious%20activity%20that%20we%20need%20to%20explore.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Feverything-we-know-about-mysterious-drones-new-jersey-new-york-2024-12%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1734223059000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F675ded90cf8d1359a2e0184a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Feverything-we-know-about-mysterious-drones-new-jersey-new-york-2024-12%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Dozens%20of%20suspected%20drones%20have%20been%20spotted%20flying%20over%20states%20on%20the%20East%20Coast%20of%20the%20United%20States%2C%20sparking%20concern%20from%20local%20officials.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22kniemeyer%40insider.com%20(Kenneth%20Niemeyer%2CJake%20Epstein%2CKatherine%20Tangalakis-Lippert)